{"tid":444644,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］初戀的定義","createTime":"2017-10-22T16:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T14:47:14.000Z","uid":154126,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b456d045331f0edcb725e4f3cdf892608f2f6c","tid":444644,"uid":154126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:06:05.000Z","msg":"初戀既定義其實係咩？<br />\n<br />\n有人話你個初吻比左邊個，邊個就係你嘅初戀。<br />\n有人話你"},{"pid":"17cb90d469d47114cfd5d9a63add77e1434b3626","tid":444644,"uid":154126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初戀既定義其實係咩？<br />\n<br />\n有人話你個初吻比左邊個，邊個就係你嘅初戀。<br />\n有人話你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人話真係一齊拍過拖，第一個令你傷心嘅人先係你嘅初戀。<br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇？<br />\n<br />\n一齊分享同回憶下自己嘅初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ff675d9b0837b0a3a8afb4261dd0a148816c44","tid":444644,"uid":150680,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:10:12.000Z","msg":"第一個同你講分手個位"},{"pid":"09a9350c97cd7d6bad189e21edbf0145da00d84c","tid":444644,"uid":154109,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:13:27.000Z","msg":"第一個令你成長嗰個伴侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ddf084cdc0b4d34411a9ae7e93bf7c2f7f2f035","tid":444644,"uid":38958,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:15:36.000Z","msg":"第一個令你相信一生一世既人<br />\n之後就會離你而去 <br />\n你呢世就唔會再信一生一世"},{"pid":"cedec29b6094451f584fbf19275e94e9463a1072","tid":444644,"uid":154126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一個令你成長嗰個伴侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同呢個伴侶一齊之前嘅人反而都唔算係初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba5750715d2dd55cab863f710fa831a704ba174","tid":444644,"uid":115724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T16:18:53.000